data.description: Vacation at home!!! Walk across the street to launch your boat on Lake Winnipesaukee from the Meredith town docks. Stroll along the waterfront and take in views of Meredith Bay. Walk to all the best waterfront dining spots in the Lakes Region. Shop, dine and relax at the Hermit Woods Winery...all a two minute walk from your 3-4 bedroom/2 bath home. Spectacular in town location, perfect for a 2nd home getaway or offset all your expenses with a vacation home rental. This home features a kitchen that opens to the dining and family room with wood floors. First floor full bath and a separate laundry room. Kitchen opens up to an optional 4th bedroom area or second family room. The second floor has three bedrooms, a full bath and an open flex area, perfect for a home office. Stay cool this summer with a new mini-split for a/c & efficient heating. Expansive front entry/mudroom. New front patio expands your outside entertaining area. New siding for maintenance free living. Oversized attached storage area, perfect for your kayaks, skis and paddleboards! Start your Staycation in this beautiful Meredith home. Showings begin at the Open House 7/31 10-1.
